102
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,433
and we've been swapping
e-mails ever since.

103
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:37,466
So what's up?

104
00:05:37,533 --> 00:05:38,966
Was he able to
help you figure out

105
00:05:39,033 --> 00:05:40,733
