many of Kokubunji's!

118
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,700
Well, if there's anything
else you need to know,

119
00:06:07,766 --> 00:06:09,433
feel free to ask
either one of us.

120
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,233
Give us a call;

121
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:11,933
we're more than
happy to help out.

122
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,900
I appreciate that.

123
00:06:13,966 --> 00:06:16,066
Oh yeah, is your Persocom okay?

124
00:06:16,133 --> 00:06:19,066
I was waiting for
you to ask me that.

125
00:06:19,133 --> 00:06:21,433
Her circuits were
all messed up, big time.

126
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:24,433
