you weren't able to fix her.

131
00:06:35,766 --> 00:06:37,700
Aye!

132
00:06:37,766 --> 00:06:40,800
I wouldn't let my little
Sumomo stay like that!

133
00:06:40,866 --> 00:06:43,666
I've put too much time
and money into her!

134
00:06:43,733 --> 00:06:47,666
It's a good thing I was careful
and backed up all her data.

135
00:06:47,733 --> 00:06:50,466
If I had to buy new parts
I woulda charged you for 'em.

136
00:06:50,533 --> 00:06:51,900
I don't have any money.

137
00:06:51,966 --> 00:06:52,966
