152
00:07:26,366 --> 00:07:28,366
I didn't know that Persocoms
could write by hand.

153
00:07:28,433 --> 00:07:29,233
You bet.

154
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:31,500
Course a printer
can also be attached.

155
00:07:31,566 --> 00:07:33,566
Then why do you have her
write by hand like that?

156
00:07:33,633 --> 00:07:35,833
She just looks
cute when she writes.

157
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:37,266
Huh, well that's kinda weird.

158
00:07:37,333 --> 00:07:39,333
