207
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,300
Oh, hi there.

208
00:09:45,366 --> 00:09:46,600
You know, if you spend your days

209
00:09:46,666 --> 00:09:47,633
in class like that,

210
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:49,466
